Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.05,0:26:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是最后一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.93,0:26:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.87,0:26:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有结婚的对象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.01,0:26:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.88,0:26:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.61,0:27:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么办    对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.68,0:27:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.09,0:27:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人把女儿美佳养大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.69,0:27:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来，作女人的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.83,0:27:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又再一次跟我说再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.54,0:28:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚觉得要和我在一起的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.75,0:28:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了别的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.75,0:28:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲话传到美佳的同龄人那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.52,0:28:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很难重新开始了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.49,0:29:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了女人的自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.69,0:29:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开开心心地过着生活，有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.50,0:29:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里有多少个房间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.64,0:29:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里很小的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.98,0:29:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一个房子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.58,0:29:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:47.71,0:29:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.32,0:29:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.99,0:29:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没有这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.59,0:29:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:55.59,0:29:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间这样子好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.39,0:29:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.46,0:30:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀树不用道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.13,0:30:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.80,0:30:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没教好女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.54,0:30:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个个都想欺负我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.88,0:30:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿美佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.48,0:30:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她的公秀树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.28,0:30:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新盖的房子到完工前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.35,0:30:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时和我住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.58,0:30:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没睡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:54.85,0:30:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点睡不着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.92,0:30:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佳睡得很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.99,0:31:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是在家里，睡得很安心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.33,0:31:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.13,0:31:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里要妳照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.53,0:31:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.67,0:31:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.08,0:31:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵闹一些才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.82,0:31:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.29,0:31:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么，一个人生活很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.50,0:31:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常会觉得寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.17,0:31:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的婚姻生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.64,0:31:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有两年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.91,0:32:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳马上会找到新的人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.72,0:32:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我家的不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.72,0:32:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.25,0:32:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.53,0:32:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多该睡了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.19,0:32:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.40,0:32:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.61,0:32:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那候，,我对秀树眼里的恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.42,0:32:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有发觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.02,0:32:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.29,0:42:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿的老公对我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.82,0:42:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.30,0:42:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我已经没有自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.83,0:42:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刺激女人的部位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.50,0:42:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.66,0:43:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我帮忙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.80,0:43:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.94,0:43:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里白住，至少要做饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.61,0:43:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那早饭就拜托啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.75,0:43:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈妳知道我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.08,0:43:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前开始就是这样了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.82,0:43:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.69,0:43:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:50.42,0:43:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚刚两年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.96,0:43:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是新婚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:55.89,0:43:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还起不了床呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:58.70,0:43:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:08.57,0:44:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.31,0:44:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:13.65,0:44:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.85,0:44:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服旧了，就买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.92,0:44:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也买了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.12,0:44:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在换季很便宜，就买了
