Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:51.33,1:56:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:54.80,1:57:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候，我的内心   充满了作为女人的自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:34.84,1:57:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去朋友那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:38.58,1:57:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚了，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:47.66,1:57:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?特产吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:57.80,1:57:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:59.93,1:58:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是做这种的，我在那里做了一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:07.28,1:58:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是妈妈的吧生日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:12.35,1:58:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘记了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:16.88,1:58:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来，受妳照顾了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:23.69,1:58:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:26.89,1:58:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个房子得到了，一起住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:33.30,1:58:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一个人在这里很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:40.11,1:58:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让妈妈一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:44.51,1:58:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要妈妈和我一起活
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:51.85,1:58:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让妳担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:57.19,1:59:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:01.86,1:59:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:08.14,1:59:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佳这样子买东西给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:12.01,1:59:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了邀请我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:15.21,1:59:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的都忘记的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:18.01,1:59:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都帮我记住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:21.08,1:59:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子我却
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:24.15,1:59:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:26.55,1:59:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶的感觉和眼泪一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:29.89,1:59:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流淌着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:32.83,1:59:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我知道后悔已经太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:37.90,1:59:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也停不下来了
